# mobius‚Äëmpd

> **M√∂bius Perspective Distortion (MPD)** augmentation for PyTorch & Albumentations  

> Chhipa, Prakash Chandra, et al. "M√∂bius transform for mitigating perspective distortions in representation learning." European Conference on Computer Vision. Cham: Springer Nature Switzerland, 2024.

# M√∂bius-MPD ‚Äî Perspective-Distortion Augmentation

